    "texte_orig": "I[SP]think[SP]the[SP]old[SP]guy's[SP]right.[1205][U+000A][SP]Being[SP]happy[SP]and\nbeing[SP]an[SP]Idealian[SP]are[SP]two[SP]different[SP]things.",
