    "texte_orig": "It[SP]does[SP]seem[SP]weird,[SP]not[SP]having[SP]any[SP]problems[SP]at\nall...[1205][U+000F][SP]It's[SP]like[SP]being[SP]dead...[1205][U+000F][SP]Or[SP]not[SP]human,\nat[SP]the[SP]very[SP]least.",
