    "texte_orig": "Hm?[SP]But[SP]you're[SP]all[SP]in[SP]perfect[SP]health.[1205][U+000F][SP]Overdoing\nit[SP]is[SP]worse[SP]than[SP]underdoing[SP]it.[1205][U+000A][SP]There's[SP]no[SP]need\nfor[SP]me[SP]to[SP]treat[SP]you.",
